additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Not to be taken. Causes skin irritation and serious eye irritation. Avoid contact with skin and eyes. Wash hands thoroughly after use. For advice contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone: Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand: 0800 764 766) or a doctor at once and have product label at hand. If swallowed: do not induce vomiting. If in eyes: holds eyelids apart and flush the eye continuously with running water. Continue flushing until advised to stop by a Poisons Information Centre or doctor, or for at least 15 minutes.
